Terrorsaur:




Terrorsaur watched from above as Inferno and the clones moved out 
from the cave. He didn't know what it was, but his keen eye sight 
told him Megatron's plan worked.

He mused. Where exactly was Megatron going with this? He took off 
from his perch and let the currents lift him into the sky. He circled 
the area, then flew off from the cave's south side. 

He wasn't sure where the clones and Inferno were going. He landed on 
a high rise, and opened his comm-link to the Predacon ship to test 
something. He said nothing into it, just let it go into the incoming 
transmittion mode.
